Install nodejs.​

Implement promise or async-await for following​

Exercise-1 :​

Create text file named file.txt​

Read file contents and then print it if file reading is successful. Otherwise, print error if file reading is not successful.​

Exercise-2:​

Install Mysql.​

Create database company.​

Create table employee with columns - id, name and designation.​

Make connection to the database​

If database connection is successful then insert the record into the database.​

Once insert is successful then display all records.​

Update the records into the database and then display updated records.​

Delete all records